snippet.title: We play Free Fall for the Apple II (Sirius Software, 1982) - Mark Turmell
snippet.description:
0:00 Title screen
1:03 Level 1 Screen 1 Girders
2:23 Level 3 Screen 1
2:45 Orange exit - bonus man
3:58 Level 1 Screen 1
4:44 Dying off the left of the screen
5:12 Level 1 Screen 2 Bibbops
6:44 New game
7:55 Another new game
8:40 Level 1 Screen 2
10:30 Level 3 Screen 1
11:28 Cheating? What cheating?
11:36 Joystick
13:25 Level 1 Screen 2
14:15 Level 1 Screen 3 Gunners!
15:15 Robbed - so close
16:03 System setup info
17:42 Level 1 Screen 2 again…
19:00 some funny ball bounces
19:28 Level 1 Screen 3
19:49 Level 2 from the start screen - fail
20:11 Level 3 from the start screen
20:37 Level 3 Screen 2
21:25 Dead
21:30 Half a year later - we start cheating
21:44 Level 1 Screen 2
22:00 Level 1 Screen 3
22:40 Level 2 Screen 1
23:24 Level 2 Screen 2
24:20 Level 2 Screen 3
25:25 Level 3 Screen 1
27:20 Level 3 Screen 2
27:30 We die lots…
29:13 Level 3 Screen 3 - last screen
30:55 We finish!!!!!!
31:30 Summing up
